        <updateDate>2019-05-31T22:10:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Officers of the Law In Civilian Establishments Act of 2019 or the POLICE Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill modifies federal restrictions on the possession of a firearm or dangerous weapon in a federal facility.</p> <p>Specifically, it permits uniformed law enforcement officers to carry agency-issued firearms and dangerous weapons in certain publicly accessible federal facilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
